name: Metaverse Magazine Edition 3
description: Edition three was launched 8/13/21, featuring work from Bitbones, Eternal Bloom, Oddcr0w, NoCreative, Pidgies, NeverAsleep, Dianave, RIFQI and Andre Vieira. Includes a custom takeover cover from YungContent and an exclusive interview with Karsen Woods. We also launch the TezRobots x Metaverse Magazine collab!
